&lt;h1&gt;Clerical Officer&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Oncology Derpartment is looking to appoint a Clerical Officer to join our B Level Oncology Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and highly motivated individual to work within the Department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to have excellent commucation skills, be flexible in your approach, be able to meet tight deadlines and like interaction with a wide variety of staff within the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role involves dealing with patients and includes receptioning in our very busy Oncology Outpatient Department. Working together and being part of a dedicated team is essential as ensuring the patient experience is paramount.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is demanding, challenging and very rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date 19/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
